WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:02.000
Do you believe

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.618
in “learning by doing”?

00:00:04.620 --> 00:00:05.720
We do!

00:00:05.721 --> 00:00:07.800
With simpleshow interactive.

00:00:07.801 --> 00:00:12.440
Our e-learning solutions combine
storytelling with interactivity.

00:00:12.441 --> 00:00:14.160
Why?

00:00:14.161 --> 00:00:16.440
Because if we see,

00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:19.160
try and explore for ourselves

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:22.720
– it just clicks!

00:00:22.721 --> 00:00:26.320
Let’s take a closer look at our interactive formats!

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:29.600
Level 1 is all about quizzes!

00:00:29.601 --> 00:00:33.160
But with us, the questions don’t feel like an exam.

00:00:33.161 --> 00:00:36.840
They engage the learner to repeat the main messages

00:00:36.840 --> 00:00:40.760
– and empower you to prove the learning success.

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:44.800
In level 2, we involve the learner even more.

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:48.880
With playful interactions he can discover your topic,

00:00:48.880 --> 00:00:54.120
understand the connections and see the big picture behind.

00:00:54.121 --> 00:00:58.640
At level 3, everything is possible.

00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:01.880
No matter if you need a full online course

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:04.000
or an innovative solution

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.480
– this level can turn any topic

00:01:06.481 --> 00:01:09.440
into an interactive learning experience.

00:01:09.441 --> 00:01:10.960
So let’s do this!

00:01:10.961 --> 00:01:12.200
Choose your favorite

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:13.960
and we will send your target group

00:01:13.961 --> 00:01:17.080
on a learning journey they’ll never forget.

